<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361471" n="1"/>
<p> Viro <abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs></p>
<p>Distuli propter negotia medico-practica responsio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem ad <abbr>eruditiss.<hi rend="sup">am</hi></abbr> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs key="B_1718-07-04_991170517053605501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1718-07-04">4 hujus mensis</date>
<lb/>datam. Nunc respondeo ad tuas novissimas <rs key="B_1718-07-27_991170517053405501" type="letter">literas</rs>
<lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <date when="1718-07-28">hac die</date> ad me deferuntur, Tibique Vir Amicissime
                              <lb/>significo mihi gratissimum fore tuum adventum
                              <lb/>in hanc <abbr>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantiss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Urbem</rs>, ubi <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> parat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>sunt pro tuo commodo et pro tua habitatione.
                              <lb/>Veni ergo pro ut Tibi libet Vir <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr> nam
                              <lb/>ego avide Te expecto. De meis rebus scilicet de
                              <lb/>iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad Te scripsi coram agemus, Tuque scripta
                              <lb/>mea revidebis <choice><sic>dataqua</sic><corr>dataque</corr></choice> necessitate corriges.</p> <closer><salute>Vale
                                    <lb/>et saluta meo nomine <abbr>D.</abbr> Agnatum Tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542472" type="person">Nico<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>laum</rs> <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobi</rs> Filium.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="B_1718-07-28_991170517053205501" type="place">Venetiis</rs>
<lb/><date when="1718-07-28"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> 28 Julii 1718.</date></dateline></closer>
      <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.en</abbr> den <date when="1718-07-29">29<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date>.</foreign></note>
</div>
